ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 167 - (Alberta) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 167 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of ALBERTA with respect to the SEVERE WILDFIRES causing the evacuation of residents and damage to public and private infrastructure in the Town of Slave Lake and the surrounding region during the month of May 2011.
